data.description: Nestled in the heart of a sought-after Northeast neighborhood, this charming one-story home offers an exceptional living experience. Boasting three spacious bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms, this residence spans 1,945 square feet of living space on a generous 7,000+ square foot lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by high wood vaulted ceilings that add character and warmth to the living area. The bay window breakfast nook is a delightful feature, providing a sunny spot for morning coffee with picturesque views. With tiled floors throughout, this home combines style and ease of maintenance. The open and spacious living room is perfect for entertaining, and the master bedroom offers ample tranquility. Outside, the front landscape is impeccably maintained, enhancing the curb appeal. Additionally, the property includes a small built-in garage office, providing a flexible space for remote work or creative pursuits. This home seamlessly blends comfort and style, creating a perfect haven to call home
